HEADWORD: Double-dyed
<hw>Dou"ble-dyed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Dyed twice;
thoroughly or intensely colored; hence; firmly fixed in opinions or
habits; <as>as, a <ex>double-dyed</ex> villain</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

